snippet.title: Screwjumper - Xbox 360 (Delisted Games Hands On)
snippet.description:
► Read more about this and hundreds of delisted titles at https://delistedgames.com/screwjumper

Take a look at the Trial Version of this early Xbox Live Arcade indie title from THQ and Frozen Codebase.

Delisting is what happens when licensing deals, studio closures and financial failures bring a downloadable game offline. Delisted Games hopes to chronicle as much of a game’s afterlife as Wikipedia does its creation and reception.
